Kayano Kaede Korosensei
Dear Korosensei,
Come to the field of zebra grass in the hills behind the school at 7 PM tonight.

00:16:42.730 --> 00:16:43.830
So you came.

00:16:44.270 --> 00:16:47.150
Let's end this, then.

00:16:50.190 --> 00:16:54.580
Korosensei, I'm the one who gave you your name, you know.

00:16:55.530 --> 00:16:58.080
So as your mother, I'll take your life, too.

00:16:58.080 --> 00:17:02.580
Kayano-san, it's too dangerous to keep using those tentacles!

00:17:02.580 --> 00:17:06.330
If you don't remove them and seek treatment immediately, your own life could be at risk!

00:17:06.330 --> 00:17:09.680
What are you talking about? They're in excellent condition.

00:17:09.680 --> 00:17:12.280
Don't even bother trying to throw me off with a bluff.

00:17:12.280 --> 00:17:13.420
Kayano...

00:17:14.300 --> 00:17:16.720
Was it all an act?

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:22.270
Even when we were having fun? Or overcoming hardship together with everyone?

00:17:23.040 --> 00:17:24.690
It was.

00:17:24.690 --> 00:17:26.550
I am an actress, after all.

00:17:27.580 --> 00:17:30.400
When Nagisa was defeated by Takaoka-sensei,

00:17:30.400 --> 00:17:33.320
I could hardly bear to watch without joining in the fight.

00:17:33.320 --> 00:17:36.910
When I was kidnapped by delinquents and kicked by the Reaper,

00:17:37.450 --> 00:17:39.510
I was so angry that I wanted to kill them on the spot.

00:17:39.910 --> 00:17:43.470
But I endured it and kept up the frail girl act.

00:17:43.470 --> 00:17:45.710
Because if my identity was exposed before I killed him,

00:17:45.710 --> 00:17:48.040
I wouldn't be able to avenge my sister.

00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:51.630
Your sister... Yukimura-sensei?

00:17:51.630 --> 00:17:56.070
Hers was truly a wretched fate, to be killed by this monster.

00:17:56.820 --> 00:17:58.980
She loved being a teacher.

00:17:59.720 --> 00:18:02.380
I heard a little about you all, too.

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:06.410
Come on, you can do it if you try!

00:18:06.410 --> 00:18:10.520
This E Class is a paradise, overflowing with dreams and opportunities!

00:18:11.060 --> 00:18:13.230
Yukimura-sensei...

00:18:13.820 --> 00:18:15.930
You wear really lame shirts sometimes, you know?

00:18:15.930 --> 00:18:19.190
What? These are my best clothes!

00:18:20.690 --> 00:18:22.760
We know, Kayano.

00:18:23.830 --> 00:18:27.980
We only had her for two short weeks in the March of our second year,

00:18:27.980 --> 00:18:30.500
but she was a passionate, shining example of a teacher.

00:18:31.630 --> 00:18:36.340
Would Korosensei kill Yukimura-sensei just like that?

00:18:36.340 --> 00:18:40.590
He's never done anything that cruel in front of us.

00:18:41.050 --> 00:18:46.060
Right? At least hear him out, Kaede-chan!

00:18:46.060 --> 00:18:50.470
He even came all the way to my house when I was suspended.

00:18:51.490 --> 00:18:54.400
But are you really okay with this?

00:18:55.010 --> 00:19:01.370
I can't imagine that what you're doing now is the best way to resolve this as an assassin.

00:19:03.120 --> 00:19:07.000
I'm guessing your body feels hot, but the nape of your neck feels cold.

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:10.000
That's the abnormal metabolism characteristic of those with implanted tentacles.

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:13.140
If you fight in that condition, you'll really be in trouble.

00:19:13.140 --> 00:19:16.030
You'll lose control amidst the heat and agony,

00:19:16.030 --> 00:19:18.420
and your life-force will be drained by the tentacles.

00:19:19.220 --> 00:19:20.280
At worst...

00:19:22.890 --> 00:19:25.850
Shut up. This is none of your business.

00:19:27.140 --> 00:19:31.550
No matter the weakness or shortcoming, anything that's polished can become a weapon.

00:19:31.550 --> 00:19:34.110
You're the one who taught me that, Sensei.

00:19:34.110 --> 00:19:36.520
If my body's too hot to bear,

00:19:36.520 --> 00:19:40.200
I'll just make it even hotter and gather the heat in my tentacles!

00:19:40.530 --> 00:19:41.660
No! Any more and—

00:19:46.560 --> 00:19:48.940
I'm in the very best condition.

00:19:48.940 --> 00:19:54.130
My whole body's so sensitive that I won't miss a single opening.

00:19:54.130 --> 00:19:55.590
Stop it, Kayano!

00:19:55.590 --> 00:19:57.050
This isn't right!

00:19:57.050 --> 00:19:58.830
I learned this lesson too!

00:19:58.830 --> 00:20:03.370
If you sacrifice yourself to kill someone, there won't be anything left behind!

00:20:04.260 --> 00:20:07.610
I'm not planning on sacrificing myself, Nagisa.

00:20:08.260 --> 00:20:09.770
All I'm doing...

00:20:10.480 --> 00:20:11.890
is killing him.

00:20:13.880 --> 00:20:16.730
Once I put my mind to something, I just keep on rolling!

00:20:21.700 --> 00:20:24.660
Wow... They're like volcanic bombs.

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:30.080
Kayano... isn't acting? These are her true feelings?

00:20:31.240 --> 00:20:34.040
I snagged a piece! It's still moving!

00:20:34.040 --> 00:20:37.130
She's only been fighting like this for ten or fifteen seconds,

00:20:37.130 --> 00:20:39.960
but the tentacles are already starting to take over her mind.

00:20:41.680 --> 00:20:43.930
What's the matter, Korosensei?

00:20:43.930 --> 00:20:46.110
My head doesn't hurt anymore!

00:20:46.110 --> 00:20:48.600
The pain feels good now!

00:20:48.600 --> 00:20:52.060
If they've already taken that much control, it's too late.

00:20:52.060 --> 00:20:54.430
Whether or not she gets her revenge,

00:20:54.430 --> 00:20:56.490
she'll only last a few more minutes after that.

00:20:57.770 --> 00:20:58.950
Then I think she'll die.

00:21:00.180 --> 00:21:01.030
